SUMMARY:Project Return - Art Sale
LOCATION:304 W. Waters Avenue Tampa \, FL 33604 United States
DESCRIPTION:May is Mental Health Awareness Month\, and here at Project Ret
 urn\, we know that art has the power to heal\, connect\, and inspire. So\,
  for this Mental Health Awareness Month\, we invite you to support our mem
 bers in recovery by attending Project Returns Art Sale Blowout on Saturday
 \, May 30th\, 2026\, from 12-2pm! Your purchase will directly support a sa
 fe\, creative space where individuals can express themselves and build com
 munity. Every piece tells a story. Come find one that speaks to you while 
 supporting Project Returns mission of hope dignity\, and support for indiv
 iduals living with mental illness. Weve slashed prices on artworks by 50 O
 FF\, and included Name-Your-Price Clearance Bins! Theres never been a bett
 er time to support Project Return and share in the overflowing creativity 
 here. \n\nPermalink: https://www.tampa.gov/node/190126
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.tampa.gov/node/190126
