DESCRIPTION:SPMOPs 2025 Photo Laureate Jesi Cason talks about her work doc
 umenting the vibrant underground world of Tampa shaped by decades of music
 \, creativity\, and subculture. Long considered a global hub for death met
 al\, the region has fostered a network of communities (goths\, punks\, rav
 ers\, and others) who have built a city within a city grounded in self-exp
 ression and belonging. \n\nPermalink: https://www.tampa.gov/node/190316
