SUMMARY:Fundamental Figure Drawing
LOCATION:120 W Gasparilla Plaza Tampa \, FL 33602 United States
DESCRIPTION:This class will teach students to capture the character\, stru
 cture\, and movement of the human figure. Students will make a 1824 tonal 
