 uities collection in order to learn core principles. Each lesson focuses o
 n using simple tools to communicate the action of the body clearly and eff
 ectively. Sundays\, May 31  Jul 12  1:004:00 PM (7 classesNo class Jun 5) 
 Ages 18  Beginner-Intermediate Level Drawing materials provided. This clas
