SUMMARY:FREE HUD Approved In person Homebuyer workshop
LOCATION:2555 E. Hanna Ave Tampa \, FL 33610 United States
DESCRIPTION:Your journey to homeownership starts here! Join us for our FRE
 E In-Person Homebuyers Workshop and learn everything you need to know abou
 t purchasing your first home\, improving your credit\, understanding the m
 ortgage process\, and accessing available down payment assistance programs
 . Up to 100\,000 in Down Payment Assistance may be available for qualified
  buyers! City of Tampa City Center 2555 E. Hanna Ave  Tampa\, Florida 3361
 0 Saturday\, July 27 8:30 AM  4:00 PM HUD-Approved Housing Counseling Agen
 cy Lunch will be provided Limited seats available  Registration is REQUIRE
 D! Take the first step toward building generational wealth and making your
  dream of homeownership a reality. Register today at: www.reach4housing.or
 g (http:www.reach4housing.org) \n\nPermalink: https://www.tampa.gov/node/1
 90521
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.tampa.gov/node/190521
