SUMMARY:Back to School Bash - New Tampa YMCA
LOCATION:16221 Compton Dr Tampa \, FL 33647 United States
DESCRIPTION:Back to School Bash at YMCA New TampaDate: July 26\, 2026  10:
 00 AM - 2:00 PMLocation: 16221 Compton Dr \,Tampa\, FL 33647Get ready to k
 ick off the new school year with our exciting Back to School Bash! Join us
  at the YMCA New Tampa for a day of celebration and preparation. School Es
 sentials:Stock up on all the supplies you need to start the school year ri
 ght! Parents can pre-register their children for a Free Backpack (while su
 pplies last) and participate in our interactive scavenger hunt to stock up
  on school supplies from all of our sponsors and vendors. Community Fun:Co
 nnect with local businesses as we come together to celebrate the back-to-s
 chool season. With healthcare\, after school programs\, community support 
 groups\, fun activities\, health insurance\, martial arts\, dancing\, and 
 sports programs. There are all sorts of resources to start the year off ri
 ght. free face painting\, \, photo stops\, fitness activities\, and health
 care resources.Mark your calendars and join us for a fantastic Back to Sch
 ool Bash at YMCA New Tampa on July26th \, 2026 from 10am to 2pm only!Paren
 ts can RSVP for backpacks while supplies last on Eventbrite(Registration c
 oming soon)For vendor or sponsorship information\, contact Lilly by email 
 at LKFloridaPenguinProductions.com or call us at 727-510-9343 \n\nPermalin
 k: https://www.tampa.gov/node/190656
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.tampa.gov/node/190656
END:VEVENT
